>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T15:21:00.000Z","msg":"無記錯呢篇研究一早畀人屌<br />\nlancet 呀嘛<br />\nwiki 有個專頁講d人亂quote篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92292957cf3594a321f5da36bf0978e8e1946f7c","tid":816932,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeff2e82363610407681f57769a253e4dacb951d","tid":816932,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a4cc00c233aac9b9ee69a388ee7ab4e4b45a586","tid":816932,"uid":138409,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a8ae2d9005445dfbdf0a7ebeaa1ccaa8793b0f4a","tid":816932,"uid":30966,"like":22,"dislike":6,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T05:20:25.000Z","msg":"ching係邊間醫學院grad?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(07\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flancet%2Farticle%2FPIIS0140-6736%2807&d=1omiQOYDo2tM%2Bh4nfUKcwjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=74c83e8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thelancet.com/journals/lancet/article/PIIS0140-6736(07</a>)60464-4/fulltext<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/162943_027422a160f16c051f15e1cd5416300c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F162943_027422a160f16c051f15e1cd5416300c.png&h=24f480d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCannabis嘅危害低過酒精同煙草啊<br />\nching係邊間醫學院grad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T15:21:00.000Z","msg":"無記錯呢篇研究一早畀人屌<br />\nlancet 呀嘛<br />\nwiki 有個專頁講d人亂quote篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T10:46:13.000Z","msg":"有無source<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上網查過評論<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2011/09/110906121953.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedaily.com%2Freleases%2F2011%2F09%2F110906121953.htm&d=1omiQOYDo2tM%2Bh4nfUKcwjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=d4d74ce5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2011/09/110906121953.htm</a><br />\n啲同行嘅評論似乎係話 <br />\n作者將個人傷害同社會傷害合埋一齊計算<br />\n比重如何拿捏 並唔應該由科學家自己決定<br />\n<br />\n／American researchers Jonathan Caulkins, Peter Reuter, and Carolyn Coulson argue that Nutt erred by assuming that drug-related harms can be reduced to a single dimension. Most such rankings combine individual harms and harms to society. But national drug policies aim to reduce harm to society, so combined scores may be misleading. Furthermore, it is not for scientists alone to decide the relative weights society should place on such disparate drug-related harms as dependence, overdose death, and corruption. ／<br />\n<br />\n但係望返啲data<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/14/184442_cd5603c67269d2251b7921c7d77fbac7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2F184442_cd5603c67269d2251b7921c7d77fbac7.png&h=8e6f4ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n酒精響<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有</span></span>指標都係比大麻嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以比重已經不重要了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點計都好<br />\n酒精都係嚴重過大麻"}]}